202b75961b3e142e5ca4","tid":455772,"uid":75984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:36:32.000Z","msg":"伊巴"},{"pid":"1f8ac49e3779b63cc5d017a62795ffd229052013","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沙基利</blockquote><br />\n今季前又話要打歐聯 估唔到最後留低 快啲走啦 喺史篤城真係唔會有太好發展"},{"pid":"1bce9a42622d86b83151e56daa2ce89b591b26e2","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Rashford</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n有速度有鬥心 罰球睇得出有苦練過 有急墜 不過佢啲傳中其實都幾準 希望佢喺英格蘭可以同卡尼擦出火花"},{"pid":"7d8c2e0ad79c3d2618d7788d8e310207f056e836","tid":455772,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:43:46.000Z","msg":"艾沙拉維"},{"pid":"f7b4cec65462f727bbbb186ab4484475118b04cc","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>J辛尼迪</blockquote><br />\nLegend<br />\n右閘 右中場 甚至中堅都打得<br />\n保養得自己好好 年紀大嗰陣都全場飛 巴爾硬爆佢 佢都好落力追 忠臣就唔使講啦"},{"pid":"a77a1d758daf177938306b6a528ddce35abe2daf","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伊巴</blockquote><br />\n好波但太自大 但相信呢樣就係大家鐘意佢嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b733ed55738e99d7c8d50f643051f426a5b201","tid":455772,"uid":23305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:46:34.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"9dbf34fb51de02fd9846c4c7fe69895bc4c999be","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Me</blockquote><br />\n搶人女友 逼走施治 十二碼一飛衝天 世界其中一個最佳門將"},{"pid":"96921e0f22229f10467e26de1375c8b5e1b8abae","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Tom Daives</blockquot