c=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8ec6f2d5bbb034ebcef2ae71d398392837cbfd","tid":455772,"uid":11311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"迪斯高"},{"pid":"208e1b3bc747c5b4c22ed3da0efa0c6debb58dd8","tid":455772,"uid":126250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"117e8f62b99d6d4eaaa5fa5aa88568a206b92824","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>布斯基斯</blockquote><br />\n影帝喺巴塞真係好重要 189cm高截波好屈 出腳快又準 保護防線 轉守為攻既重要人物 控波唔會控死 令到中場好流暢 <br />\n哥帥重用佢 逼走yaya<br />\n仲要30歲都未夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c8fa0f18e6fe497dd48e33c54bbce2aa04b786","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>史高斯</blockquote><br />\nBest playmaker ever in the EPL<br />\n重炮 長傳 短傳 皆精<br />\n長傳(driven pass)"},{"pid":"1e02c1f31e0427583379b775dd4f98c92605b7c1","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>史高斯</blockquote><br />\nBest playmaker ever in the EPL<br />\n重炮 長傳 短傳 皆精<br />\n長傳(driven pass)</blockquote><br />\n斬個波速度好快 轉邊嘅節奏好迅速<br />\n透過1 2去掌控中場 無處不在"},{"pid":"90124fb0f34b75530e045efa9185b1e461ee08a2","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迪斯高</blockquote><br />\n你基本上已經分別喺德甲 英超 意甲證明自己 <br />\n係神鋒嘅級數 <br />\n做target man 又得<br />\n腳下功夫又唔錯(中鋒嚟講)<br />\n同利雲同一個級數"},{"pid":"079a525e5c05af7fc5352d5f6d96d7b303e0c837","tid":455772,"uid":24708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:33:29.000Z","msg":"Marko Marin"},{"pid":"b80577ebe9f19ba4641d66d5a051b8150adcc223","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-1