18:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天使<br />\nisco</blockquote><br />\n天使喺皇馬時打左翼真係好有效率<br />\n14歐聯決賽有球自己左邊扭入去1打3 射完撲到 巴爾補中<br />\n揀錯英超 太體力化<br />\nisco根本13年加盟嗰陣已經好勁 但安帥唔用 好多謝拖舟俾機會佢去發揮 有能力喺西班牙繼承小白"},{"pid":"e63a604419bffc2654976fffa5e54a5255bebec8","tid":455772,"uid":2756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:51:10.000Z","msg":"Me呢"},{"pid":"319207f5c0ab149b49e2ccf0b359827b8fae8a3b","tid":455772,"uid":144513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T18:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Me呢</blockquote><br />\n唉 佢走去車仔其實係肥賓逼嘅 因為要重建<br />\n對曼聯空門唔入真係唔怪得佢 因為左腳射失重心<br />\n俾人笑到冇晒信心<br />\n但其實佢喺車仔奪歐聯嗰年好大貢獻<br />\n首先四強對巴單刀過埋VV射入奠勝<br />\n到決賽8x分鐘搏到個角球 Drogba頂入<br />\n大賽球員 08euro決賽跑赢lahm奠勝<br />\n人生贏家 乜都贏過<br />\n又靚仔"},{"pid":"4392a9d66eb8b67b3455113b71ef657f21fcbe45","tid":455772,"uid":155765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T19:00:08.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"cfcb74a61cff7fc3b0821deebc7c792415ffa874","tid":455772,"uid":89808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T19:04:05.000Z","msg":"Bakambu <br />\nVietto"},{"pid":"aef7bd1f56241575f8cd3c782bcd0b0d1289d614","tid":455772,"uid":74433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T19:06:11.000Z","msg":"Lampard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56bd3654b478b5ab4a6ffc56eda37f99c8709512","tid":455772,"uid":65239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T19:08:57.000Z","msg":"Mata!"},{"pid":"14d324be87df618ed4bea7952e43d005a87d6503","tid":455772,"uid":68320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T19:09:04.000Z","msg":"Dempsey<br />\nDembele"},{"pid":"b854ecde65d51ded1fdd1914d1e40accd4d2500d","tid":455772,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T19:09:05.000Z","msg":"路斯基"},{"pid":"0eec8fc803a40984963290c22b0e47764df96698","tid":455772,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"